s.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Daily Digests</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Providers get convenient next-day schedules by email.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Smart Management</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Confirm, reschedule, cancel appointments. Auto-cancel unpaid bookings.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"><div class="transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 -translate-x-10 lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Payments and billing integrated with appointment scheduling" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F